  "page": "Tyria",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Slavers_Bay.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Tyria is located in Slaver&#39;s Bay\"><img alt=\"Tyria is located in Slaver&#39;s Bay\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/09/Slavers_Bay.png/300px-Slavers_Bay.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"297\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/09/Slavers_Bay.png/450px-Slavers_Bay.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/09/Slavers_Bay.png/600px-Slavers_Bay.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 68.9%; left: 26.1%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -4px; top: -4px; width: 8px; font-size: 8px; z-index:100;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/8px-Red_pog.png\" title=\"Tyria\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/12px-Red_pog.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/16px-Red_pog.png 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size:&#160;%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; left: 0.5em; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\">Tyria</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\"><a href=\"/index.php/Slaver%27s_Bay\" title=\"Slaver&#39;s Bay\">Slaver's Bay</a> and the location of Tyria\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><b>Tyria</b> is a ruined city in <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a>. It lies across the <a href=\"/index.php/Smoking_Sea\" title=\"Smoking Sea\">Smoking Sea</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/Oros\" title=\"Oros\">Oros</a> and is connected by <a href=\"/index.php/Valyrian_road\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Valyrian road\">Valyrian road</a> to the city of <a href=\"/index.php/Valyria\" title=\"Valyria\">Valyria</a>, which lies to the south of the island.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tyria&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Tyria was founded by the <a href=\"/index.php/Valyrian_Freehold\" title=\"Valyrian Freehold\">Valyrian Freehold</a>. Although rich and glorious, it did not have self-rule and was instead governed by men and women sent from <a href=\"/index.php/Valyria\" title=\"Valyria\">Valyria</a> to rule in the name of the Freehold.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_free_cities.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_free_cities.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> \n</p><p>The ruins of Tyria are still inhabited to some extent after the <a href=\"/index.php/Doom_of_Valyria\" title=\"Doom of Valyria\">Doom of Valyria</a>, although it is not clear whether by descendants of its original inhabitants. The few stories told of these latter-day dwellers tend towards the malign.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_ancient_history:_the_doom_of_valyria.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_ancient_history:_the_doom_of_valyria.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tyria&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/Map_of_Valyria_(A_Dance_with_Dragons)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Map of Valyria (A Dance with Dragons)\">Map of Valyria</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_free_cities.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_free_cities.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Free Cities.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_ancient_history:_the_doom_of_valyria.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_ancient_history:_the_doom_of_valyria.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Ancient History: The Doom of Valyria.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403125729\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.029 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.031 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 736/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 12324/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 3538/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1675/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 13/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1448/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   22.309      1 -total\n 61.66%   13.756      1 Template:Location_map\n 58.46%   13.043      1 Template:Location_map+\n 44.85%   10.006      1 Templat